column5: Looking at this lake for a possible 2nd trip this year. any info would be very helpful. thanks Halfmoon

Reports on fishing wetenagami are few and far between on the net but you can find them. It's on my list of places to go so I've been searching reports on it for a few years. The limited info I can find is pretty positive, especially on the isolated / peaceful / beautiful place front.
Thanks sure looks good on the outfitters brochure.
